VARIOUS DEVELOPMENT PERIODS, SOMETIMES EXCEEDING FIVE YEARS. THE

EXTERNAL FACTORS THAT IMPACT THE DURATION OF A PROJECT INCLUDE

SCOPE AND COMPLEXITY, REMOTENESS OR ADVERSE OPERATING

