REVIEW OF

ONGOING EXPLORATION AND PRODUCTION ACTIVITIES IN KEY

AREAS

CHEVRONS 2011 KEY UPSTREAM ACTIVITIES, SOME OF WHICH ARE

ALSO DISCUSSED IN MANAGEMENTS DISCUSSION AND ANALYSIS OF

FINANCIAL CONDITION AND RESULTS OF OPERATIONS, BEGINNING ON

PAGE FS-2,

