D)

ASIA

IN ASIA, THE COMPANY IS ENGAGED IN UPSTREAM ACTIVITIES IN

AZERBAIJAN, BANGLADESH, CAMBODIA, CHINA, INDONESIA, KAZAKHSTAN,

MYANMAR, THE PARTITIONED ZONE LOCATED BETWEEN SAUDI ARABIA AND

