OF THE INITIAL PHASE OF THE PROJECT IS EXPECTED IN 2013, WITH PLANNED MAXIMUM TOTAL NATURAL GAS PRODUCTION OF 558 MILLION CUBIC FEET PER DAY. PROVED RESERVES HAVE BEEN RECOGNIZED FOR THIS PROJECT. THE PSC FOR CHUANDONGBEI EXPIRES IN 2037.

